creator: Hans Christian Andersen
description:
LibriVox recording of Hans Christian Andersen: Fairytales and Short Stories Volume 4, 1854 to 1859 by Hans Christian Andersen.

Read in English by Katia Bodiou; Greg Giordano; Anastasiia Solokha; Kristin Gjerløw; Jennifer Dorr; Erin Lottes; caromopfen; Slawek; Anna Simon; Claire Schreuder; KHand; Larry Wilson; Michelle Tan; HannahBanana; Zachary Brewster-Geisz; KathleenLarberg

A collection of some of Hans Christian Andersen's works. He is a Danish author and poet most famous for his fairy tales. (Summary by Kristingj)

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
